dct_title_s: Mapa general de España / formado y publicado por el Instituto Geográfico Nacional.
dct_description_sm: Shows cities and towns, roads, railways, borders, and airports. Relief shown by shading. Depths shown by bathymetric tints and isolines. "Gobierno de España,  Ministerio de Transportes, Movilidad y Agenda Urban"--Upper left corner. Includes flags, location map, and 1 ancillary map: Islas Canarias.
